		<h2>Docpad</h2>
		<p>DocPad (like Jekyll) is a static website generator, unlike Jekyll it's written in CoffeeScript+Node.js instead of Ruby, and also allows the template engine complete access to the document model. This means you have unlimited power as a CMS and the simplicity of a notepad.</p>
		<p><a class="btn" href="https://github.com/balupton/docpad">Visit Website</a></p>
